Network layer security protects internal communication channels and segmentation.

Real-life examples:

* VNets separating environments
* VPN tunnels for branch offices
* NSGs restricting subnet communication
* ExpressRoute private connectivity

For example, a company isolates HR systems from development systems.

A real-life use case is hybrid cloud enterprise networking.

Another example is secure branch office communication.

Network security limits lateral movement and secures traffic flow.
